Base Functional App Requirements (75/100)
1. Program presents a file dialog to the user to select a PDF file to read
2. Support resume/pause functionality such that playback of the file may be
paused and resumed at any time.
3. Support Stop/Load functionality such that the playback can be stopped and
another file loaded.
4. User Interface is to be graphical in nature with buttons, dropdowns, dialogs, etc.,
That said the design is open to the student’s own wishes.
5. Code should be commented at a developer’s level

Options (max 25 points):
1. Support multiple voices (10 points) 
2. Dark/Light UI selection (10 points):)
3. Play and Remaining Time Display (10 points) :)
4. Slider to go forward and backward in playback (10 points) :)
5. Display Current File (10 points) :)
6. Drag-n-Drop File Reading (15 points)
7. A Feature of Your Choosing (10 points – subject to my approval. Ask before
working on it!)

